.TH devin-help-cloud-drs 1  "drs " 
.SH NAME
devin\-help\-cloud\-drs \- Manage Declarative Repo Setup (environment blueprints, sandbox sessions, and builds)
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBdevin help cloud drs\fR [\fIsubcommands\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Manage Declarative Repo Setup (environment blueprints, sandbox sessions, and builds)
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
devin\-help\-cloud\-drs\-whoami(1)
Print the current DRS configuration (org, API endpoint, auth status)
.TP
devin\-help\-cloud\-drs\-sandbox\-create(1)
Create a sandbox Devin session for testing repo setup
.TP
devin\-help\-cloud\-drs\-run(1)
Run a shell command inside a sandbox session
.TP
devin\-help\-cloud\-drs\-blueprint\-list(1)
List all environment blueprints for the organization
.TP
devin\-help\-cloud\-drs\-blueprint\-create(1)
Create a new environment blueprint
.TP
devin\-help\-cloud\-drs\-blueprint\-write(1)
Update an existing environment blueprint
.TP
devin\-help\-cloud\-drs\-build(1)
Trigger an environment build and wait for it to finish
.TP
devin\-help\-cloud\-drs\-build\-start(1)
Trigger an environment build without waiting
.TP
devin\-help\-cloud\-drs\-build\-wait(1)
Wait for a previously started build to finish
.TP
devin\-help\-cloud\-drs\-build\-logs(1)
Fetch the log stream for a build job
.TP
devin\-help\-cloud\-drs\-secret\-create(1)
Create an organization\-level secret
